<CENTER>
<H1>Images from <BR>
"Hawaii's Search for Sovereignty"</H1>
<STRONG>Christian Science Monitor, October 17, 1994</STRONG>
<P>
(Go to <STRONG>article</STRONG> <A HREF="csmgif.html">with images</A> or with <A HREF="csm.html">
