<H1>The Overthrow of the Monarchy</H1>

<STRONG>By Pat Pitzer</STRONG><BR>
<STRONG>''Spirit of Aloha,'' May 1994</STRONG><BR>
(The in-flight magazine of Aloha Airlines)
<P>
