Kingdom of Hawai`i Constitutions: <A HREF="constitution-1840.html">1840</A> - <A HREF="constitution-1852.html">1852</A> - <A HREF="constitution-1887.html">1887</A> - <A HREF="constitution-1893.html">1893</A></CENTER>
