<DOCHDR>
http://www.hawaii-nation.org:80/nation/canoe/niu.html 204.94.112.149 19970120091009 text/html 8195
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 09:09:30 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 8024
