     <FONT SIZE=+2>T</FONT>he Japan Climatic Data Center (<A HREF = "/jcdc/jcdc/jcdc.html">JCDC</A>) was established in the Japan Meteorological Agency (<I>JMA</I>) in June 1990 to manage climate data for monitoring the global climatic change.
