<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of Azores Monthly Mean CO2
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>
<IMG SRC="/wdcgg/SiteLocation/AzoresLocation.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
Azores, Portugal
</H2></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : December 1979 - January 1992
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Azores, Terceira Island       <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Portugal                 <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 38&#176; 45&#180; N                     <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 27&#176; 05&#180; W                     <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 30 m                          <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : DOD/USAF
</PRE>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="10">
<TR><TD>
<IMG SRC="AzoresNoaa-CO2.gif">
</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<PRE>
