<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of Cape Grim Monthly Mean CO2
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>
<IMG SRC="/wdcgg/SiteLocation/CapeGrimLocation.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
Cape Grim, Australia
</H1></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : April 1984 - December 1993
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Cape Grim           <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Australia                <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  :  40&#176; 41&#180; S          <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 144&#176; 41&#180; E          <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 94 m                <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : CSIRO, Division of Atmospheric Research
</PRE>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="10">
<TR><TD>
<IMG SRC="CapeGrimNoaa-CO2.gif">
</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>
