<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : October 1993 - December 1993
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Dwejra Point        <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Malta                   <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 36&#176; 03&#180; N           <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 14&#176; 11&#180; E           <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 30 m                <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : Ministry of Environment
</PRE>
