<B>Latitude</B>  : 35&#176; 21&#180; N                 <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 77&#176; 23&#180; W                 <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
