<PRE>
        The following is an explanatory note, though a little modified, cited by the WDCGG from the
explanatory note of the NOAA Flask Network.

        NOAA/CMDL has attempted to provide the most accurate and precise measurements possible in a
timely manner.   NOAA/CMDL reserves the right to adjust the data based on recalibrations of reference
