</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Hegyhatsal          <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Hungary                  <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 46&#176; 58&#180; N           <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 16&#176; 23&#180; E           <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
