<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of Iza&ntilde;a Monthly Mean CO2
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>
<IMG SRC="/wdcgg/SiteLocation/Izana-NOAALocation.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
Iza&ntilde;a, Spain
</H1></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : November 1991 - December 1993
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Iza&ntilde;a, Tenerife           <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Spain                    <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 28&#176; 18&#180; N                 <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 16&#176; 29&#180; W                 <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 2300 m                    <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : Iza&ntilde;a Observatory
</PRE>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="10">
<TR><TD>
<IMG SRC="IzanaNoaa-CO2.gif">
</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<PRE>
        The following is an explanatory note, though a little modified, cited by the WDCGG from the
explanatory note of the NOAA Flask Network.

