<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of Ocean Station "M" Monthly Mean CO2
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>
<IMG SRC="/wdcgg/SiteLocation/OceanStationMLocation.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
Ocean Station "M", Norway
</H1></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : June 1985 - December 1993
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Ocean Station "M"      <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Norway                   <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 66&#176; 00&#180; N              <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> :  2&#176; 00&#180; E              <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 7 m                    <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : Norway Meteorological Institute
