<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of St. Croix Monthly Mean CO2
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>
<IMG SRC="/wdcgg/SiteLocation/StCroixLocation.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
St. Croix, USA
</H1></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : March 1979 - August 1990
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : St. Croix, Virgin Islands    <B>Country/Trretory</B> : USA                      <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 17&#176; 45&#180; N                    <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 64&#176; 45&#180; W                    <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 3 m                          <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : Fairleigh Dickinson University
</PRE>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="10">
<TR><TD>
<IMG SRC="StCroixNoaa-CO2.gif">
</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<PRE>
