<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of Syowa Station Monthly Mean CO2
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<H2>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Syowa Station, Antarctica<BR>
</P></H2>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : February 1986 - December 1993
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Syowa Station       <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Antarctica               <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 69&#176; 00&#180; S           <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : NDIR
<B>Longitude</B> : 39&#176; 35&#180; E           <B>Unit</B>             : ppmv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : WMO X85 Scale
<B>Altitude</B>  : 11 m                <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : Tohoku University (Japan)
</PRE>
<BR><BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="10">
<TR><TD>
<IMG SRC="SyowaStationNoaa-CO2.gif">
</TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>
