    Memo. ERL CMDL-4</I>, NOAA ERL, Boulder, Colorado, 88pp.
Steele, L.P., P.J. Fraser, R.A. Rasmussen, M.A.K. Khalil, T.J. Conway, A.J. Crawford, R.H. Gammon, K.A. Masarie
    and K.W. Thoning, 1987: The global distribution of methane in the troposphere. <I>J. Atmos. Chem,</I> 5, 125-171.
Steele, L.P. and P.M. Lang, 1991: Atmospheric methane concentrations-the NOAA/CMDL global cooperative
    flask sampling network, 19983-19988, ORNL/CDIAC-42, NDP-038.
Steele, L.P., E.J. Dlugokencky, P.M. Lang, P.P. Tans, R.C. Martin and K.A. Masarie, 1992: Slowing down
    of the global accumulation of atmospheric methane during the 1980's,. <I>Nature</I>, 358, 313.


