<HEAD>
<TITLE>
WDCGG - Trends of Mahe Island Monthly Mean CH4
</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>
<IMG SRC="/wdcgg/SiteLocation/MaheIslandLocation.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE>
Mahe Island Station, Seychelles
</H1></CENTER>
<BR><BR>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Covering period : May 1983 - December 1993
</P>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Station</B>   : Mahe Island               <B>Country/Trretory</B> : Seychelles               <B>Submmited by</B> : NOAA/CMDL
<B>Latitude</B>  : 04&#176; 40&#180; S                 <B>Time Interval</B>    : By Event                 <B>Analysis</B>     : GC-FID
<B>Longitude</B> : 55&#176; 10&#180; E                 <B>Unit</B>             : ppbv                     <B>Calibration</B>  : Gravimetric Standard
<B>Altitude</B>  : 3 m                       <B>Classification</B>   : Provisional              <B>Facility</B>     : New Mexico State University/Physical Science Laboratory
</PRE>
