<HEAD>
<title>
JCDC/JMA
</title>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<HR SIZE=5>
<H2>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Japan Climatic Data Center
</P></H2>
<HR SIZE=5>
<BR>

<FONT SIZE=+2>T</FONT>he major activities of the Japan Climatic Data Center(JCDC) are: collection of data on climate data and greenhouse gases, the comprehensive management of the collected data, and the distribution of the analysis and investigation results to users such as governmental organizations, universities and other research institutes.
<BR>

<OL>
<H2>
<LI>Data collection
</H2>
<FONT SIZE=+2>T</FONT>he JCDC collects climate data, such as temperature in the surface air, temperature and humidity in the upper air and sea surface temperature, for the purpose of monitoring the global climatic change.
<p>

<H2>
<LI>Data processing
</H2>
<FONT SIZE=+2>T</FONT>he collected data are managed in the JCDC data base system.   The JCDC analyzes the collected data for the investigation of the global climatic change.
<p>

<H2>
<LI>Data distribution
</H2>
<FONT SIZE=+2>T</FONT>he JCDC distributes climate data and annual reports to user.<p>
</OL>
<p>

<HR SIZE=10>
<CENTER>
<H3>| <A HREF="../../../jcdc.html">Home</A> | <A HREF="/jcdc/jcdc/RoleOfJMA.html">Role of the JMA</A> | <A HREF="/jcdc/Temperature/Temperature.html">Surface Temperature</A> | <A HREF="/jcdc/GreenhouseGases/GreenhouseGases.html">Trends of Atmospheric GHGs</A> | <A HREF="/jcdc/JICA/jica.html">JICA Lecture Notes</A> |
</H3></CENTER>
<HR SIZE=10>

